column1: "If the installation prices are too high for me then the consultation time is really not effective at all"
"I just want to know your installation prices. Do you work within a fixed budget? Or how does that work?"
"Wanted to know the estimated prices for something similar"
"Do I need to book an appointment to learn about estimated prices ?"
"Is there any fixed price like you take.... \nFor decorating room is there any prices fixed as per Square feet?"
"Apnader shuti pordar details ki ektu deya jabe?"
"i need you to do a project for me"
"You will give me an interior design including bathroom"
"Koto taka nen apnara ekta room  online interior design korte?"
"I need a design for my living room and kitchen"
"2800 tk ar bisoita aktu bujia bolben please."
"Amar ekta room er modhe studio plus office korbo. Oita sajaite koto lagte pare"
"Apnara kivabe ki koren jodi amr sathe contact korten tahole bujhtam"
"Do you have indoor plants decorations? Price? Picture"
"Ami ekta room er khorch somporke jante chaii. Choto room square feet ta ami bolte parbo na sevabe.. Kintu chotoi."
"Room er furniture deya e. Wall deya r tuktak decorations er moto korte chaile kmn khoroch porbe"
"I live in khulna. I want to some intetior of my flat at nirala khulna."
"3D design korte cost kmn nen for 3500sqf apt?"
"I want to arrange ny office room"
"This is my brother Ashraful's number 01677808292. You can contact him for the rest of the process as I am not in Bangladesh at the moment. Thanks!"
"Ami amr doings room ta interior korta cachhi olpo bajet modde"
"The room is it still in the process of being constructed and wanted to know if we can some suggestions/ideas.Thanks!"
"The room that I am referring to won't be in your typical building type setting."
"Do you happen to provide any services related to designing a small 300 sqft executive office room?"
"It's difficult for me to get 7 points??????"
"How can you do online?\nWithout visiting the place"
"But how much you will charge for the decorate my lobby and drawing room. All r there just to arrangements in a better way"
"What are the 7 points to decorate the House"
"I need some suggestion of room interior"
